name: The Challenge: USA
overview: Reality titans from the CBS universe compete in the most unpredictable and demanding game of their lives. With an ever-changing game, players are in a constant state of paranoia, unable to trust anyone but themselves. The CBS all-stars compete for a chance to join the upcoming global “War of the Worlds” championship.
tagline: 28 reality legends compete to be America's best.

episodes.name: The United States of Challenge
episodes.overview: BMX Legend TJ Lavin welcomes 28 competitors from Survivor, Big Brother, The Amazing Race, and Love Island to The Challenge. With old rivalries, new alliances, messy exes, and fractured friendships under one roof, who will be the first eliminated?

episodes.name: Oh Say Can You See Tiffany
episodes.overview: The Challengers are shocked by TJ's latest twist. A Survivor legend looks to cement their dominance in the game, while a crafty Big Brother player might be proving a little too popular with other Challengers.

episodes.name: Declarations of Independence
episodes.overview: While some alliances are growing in strength, others are starting to fall apart. A powerful duo starts to raise suspicions in the game, while a pair of newly mismatched Challengers' lack of team chemistry puts their games in serious danger.

episodes.name: Liberty and Justice for All
episodes.overview: TJ introduces the players to one of his favorite challenges - trivia! A vendetta from the past reignites in the Compound as a challenger seeks the ultimate revenge.

episodes.name: In Tyson We Trust
episodes.overview: The most difficult water-based challenge of the season so far leaves some players swimming to survive the game, and whispers in the compound threaten to destroy a mighty alliance.

episodes.name: A Civil War
episodes.overview: In the wake of a shocking blindside, players scramble for power and a pair of underdogs must choose between creating chaos or playing it safe.

episodes.name: State of the Unions
episodes.overview: Players are blindfolded and must navigate an epic crash course driving challenge.

episodes.name: Independence Day
episodes.overview: After a game-changing twist, a secret alliance makes plans to take control of the game.

episodes.name: Nevertheless She Persisted
episodes.overview: A vengeful player looks for payback after being sabotaged in the challenge. The reveal of a secret alliance turns the game upside down.

episodes.name: Pledges of Allegience
episodes.overview: Players must scale a moving semi-truck in one of the most intense and fast-moving challenges of the season. A ruthless player schemes to pit two allies against each other.

episodes.name: Home of the Brave
episodes.overview: The remaining players fight to secure spots in the fast-approaching Final. Who will survive the brutal conditions and TJ's twists and turns to earn the Challenge USA crown and $500,000?

episodes.name: The Riskiest Season Yet
episodes.overview: The 18 reality titans from "Big Brother," "Survivor," and "The Amazing Race" are shocked to learn that they are competing amongst six legendary veterans from MTV's "The Challenge"; a new twist puts multiple players at risk at the first elimination.

episodes.name: Blurred Battle Lines
episodes.overview: The challengers battle it out in a difficult water challenge; a new alliance is formed to target a veteran; romance blossoms between two teammates.

episodes.name: Civil War
episodes.overview: The challengers compete in a difficult swimming challenge; a vet turns on one of their own in an act of self-preservation.

episodes.name: Double Crossed and Sideswiped
episodes.overview: A shocking double elimination leaves the challengers scrambling to win a high-stakes, adrenaline filled semitruck challenge to ensure their survival in the game.

episodes.name: Operation Hat Trick
episodes.overview: "The Challenge" vets come up with a plan to take advantage of a growing rift among the rookies, resulting in one of the most shocking hopper results of the season.

episodes.name: A Really Good Looking Underdog
episodes.overview: Things get heated between two rookie players; the competitors brace themselves for host TJ Lavin's favorite challenge of the season, trivia.

episodes.name: Give Me Liberty, or Give Me Love
episodes.overview: A pair of "Challenge" vets play cupid as romance blossoms for a couple of former "Big Brother" houseguests; TJ makes a shocking announcement that impacts the game for the remainder of the season.

episodes.name: Independence Day
episodes.overview: The game takes a dramatic turn when TJ announces that teams are no more, strategy shifts for several players, and a shocking draw from the hopper forces two ride or die allies to go head to head in one of the most grueling eliminations yet.

episodes.name: Enemy of the State
episodes.overview: Michaela sets her sights on a fellow "Survivor" player who could be a threat to her game.

episodes.name: A Less Perfect Union
episodes.overview: With the news of another double elimination, the remaining players grapple with tough decisions: betraying friendships or risking elimination. The Survivors navigate the departure of a valued member, and the loss of trust in another.

episodes.name: The Slippery Business
episodes.overview: Michaela's sudden decision to target a fellow alliance member leaves Chanelle and Desi to question if she has their best interests at heart. Also, Michele finds herself in the middle between two alliances, ultimately betraying one of them.

episodes.name: Revenge Amongst the Ruins
episodes.overview: When an unexpected winner emerges from the challenge ruins, tables are turned and all alliances scramble to navigate this new power dynamic. Tempers flare and lines are drawn for against one player after a last minute voting decision.
